englishTranslationText:
They	urge	you	to	hasten	the	punishment;	
and	indeed	hell	has	encompassed	the	
disbelievers.

And	many	creatures	walk	upon	the	earth	
that	do	not	carry	their	own	sustenance;	
Allah	provides	the	sustenance	to	them	and	to	you;	and	only	He	is	the	All	Hearing,	the	All	Knowing.

In	order	to	be	ungrateful	for	Our	favours;	
and	to	use	the	comforts;	therefore	they	
will	soon	come	to	know.

 In	order	to	reward	those	who	believed	
and	did	good	deeds,	by	His	munificence;	
indeed	He	does	not	like	the	disbelievers.
